    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/2a850c22cc6a7c681794162f4fd5f9b3.avif?t=1763156628\" alt=\"\"width=1170 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you want to create beautiful tiny cities without spending all of your time into resource management?<br>Then Mini Worlds is the toy for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/7eb1413e26d4e282660a278edf3ef79f.webp?t=1763156628\" alt=\"Generate\" width=250 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your brand new world with freshly generated terrain. Each one is unique and can be customized to fit your cozy towns. From rolling hills to peaceful lakes. Start in a dense oak forest or on flowery plains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/0ed5b3870e776e4236df01c9e1fb2270.poster.avif?t=1763156628\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/0ed5b3870e776e4236df01c9e1fb2270.webm?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/0ed5b3870e776e4236df01c9e1fb2270.mp4?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/03baedbf6b83ac1ec052f3a3e465630a.webp?t=1763156628\" alt=\"Build\" width=250 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place cozy houses, winding roads and sturdy walls to give shape to your cities. If you like tiny towns or bustling cities, small community gardens or big wheat fields, Mini Worlds has the tools for you to build it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/ad89a000fc21f6123865301fad972eff.poster.avif?t=1763156628\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/ad89a000fc21f6123865301fad972eff.webm?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/ad89a000fc21f6123865301fad972eff.mp4?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/07750045ae6dc84c563c924eaab8b8e8.webp?t=1763156628\" alt=\"Decorate\" width=250 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add gentle touches to bring life to your worlds. Add gardens to houses, create parks in your cities or simply place lights to make the night-time less dim. It is all up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/ff2121c31f0ffd97be46ce26e72c006b.poster.avif?t=1763156628\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/ff2121c31f0ffd97be46ce26e72c006b.webm?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/ff2121c31f0ffd97be46ce26e72c006b.mp4?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/d02719e77722bbcb1bb8d1d80d63f77e.webp?t=1763156628\" alt=\"No Goals\" width=250 height=50 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini Worlds has no goals and no timers. It is all about relaxing and creating your own world in your own time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/a33be0c46fdbeeff245831f82000d535.poster.avif?t=1763156628\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/a33be0c46fdbeeff245831f82000d535.webm?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019950/extras/a33be0c46fdbeeff245831f82000d535.mp4?t=1763156628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mini Worlds is inspired by beautiful games like:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Islanders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fabledom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kingdoms and Castles</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Team, Only Hobby</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by solo developer Pieter Jagersma. Using my spare time to create this toy as a hobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am happy to receive constructive feedback of all kinds, so feel free to join the community. I will try my best to respond to messages and fix any problems as soon as I can.</p>",
